  <h1>玻璃管</h1>
  <h3>来源</h3>
  <text>
    <style color="0xaaaaaa" italic="true" pwt="true">注释：本页转载于MCMOD的GTCEu维基<br/>作者：<style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/119280/">Oganesson897</style>，<style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" underlined="true" url-link="https://github.com/Yefancy">KilaBash</style><br/></style>
  </text>
  <text>玻璃管可以在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/forming_press" underlined="true">冲压机床</style>或<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/alloy_smelter" underlined="true">合金炉</style>中用玻璃粉和<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:misc/mold" underlined="true">模具（球）</style>制成，或在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/fluid_solidifier" underlined="true">流体固化器</style>中用液态玻璃制成，每生产1根玻璃管就要消耗1块玻璃材料。玻璃管只需要LV电压就可以制造。<br/><br/>玻璃管可用来制作<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/vacuum_tube" underlined="true">真空管</style>，真空管是第一个电路的主要部件。</text>
